name: GDG Cloud Atlanta 2019 Kickoff Meetup!!

venue.name: Google Atlanta HQ
venue.address_1: Google Atlanta  - 10 10th Street NE #600 Atlanta, GA 30309

description:
Details:

Come join us at the Google Atlanta office on January 23rd to kick off our Atlanta GDG chapter for Google Cloud! Please register here so we can get you in the building: http://bit.ly/GDGATL_form .

The theme for the night will be building products/solutions utilizing Google Cloud’s ML/AI components.
- We’ll demo how AutoML Vision can be used to automatically build/train an ML model used to detect skin disease.
- We’ll follow that with presentations from both Farmwave and Engage Talent on how they’ve integrated Google AI/ML into their solutions.
- To round out the night, we’ll have a panel discussion with Craig Ganssle (CEO, Farmwave), Robby Gulri (CMO of Engage Talent), and Google ML experts.

We’ll provide food and drinks.

Look forward to seeing you there!

Agenda
6:00 - 6:30 PM Networking

6:30 - 6:40 PM Introductions/Opening Remarks - Craig/Mike

6:40 - 7:00 PM AutoML Vision (Slides + Demo) - Mike

7:00 - 7:15 PM Farmwave Presentation - Craig Ganssle

7:15 - 7:30 PM Engage Presentation - Robby Gulri

7:30 - 8:30 PM Panel Discussion - Craig Ganssle, Robby Gulri, Sanjay Agravat, TBD

8:30 - 9:00 PM Closing Remarks/Networking
how_to_find_us: Parking is available in the attached parking deck off of West Peachtree for a fee.  Marta is also an option as the office is directly across from the Midtown station.  Once in the building, take the elevators to the 6th floor.
